captions.text: [MUSIC PLAYING]
-Hey, guys.
It's Brooklyn and Bailey.

So this Saturday,
we had our meetup
at P.S. from Aeropostale.

And it was crazy, because
that morning we looked out
the window and there was--
-Ice and snow and sleet--

-And rain, and crazy things
were going on outside--
-All over the roads--

-And we were, like, really
worried about the people coming
and for their safety.

For everyone and everything,
we were very worried.
But the meetup went great.
Thank you all for coming.

We had so much fun
seeing you guys.

And for the people that couldn't
come because of the roads,

we hope that we will be able
to meet you again sometime.

-It was just-- the rain and the
snow and the ice, it was crazy.

-There's like 120
stores in the mall.

Out of those 150-- 120--
90 of them were closed.
-Yeah, it was that bad.

-So it was like-- we
were, like, terrified.
Like, it's Texas.
It never snows down here.

-But then it's,
like, 72 today, so--
-Go figure.
It's, like, so bipolar.

Apparently it's supposed to
snow again tomorrow, so--
-Yeah.

72 to snowing to ice to
72 to summer to spring.
Let's figure this out, guys.
-I know, I don't understand.

But, you know
what, it went well,

and we're so excited
for the next one.
Here is the recap of Saturday.
[MUSIC PLAYING]

-Thank you guys so much
for watching this video.

We were super excited, and had
so much fun doing this meetup.

And there was some fun stuff,
and some perks we got to do.
-Oh, yeah.

-And we got to shop through
some of the Aeropostale clothes,

including the new
Bethany Mota collection.

-This is one of the
things that I found.

It's a sweater, and
it's super comfortable.

Especially with all of this cold
weather, it works perfectly.

All this rain and ice and
snow that we're getting.

-And I bought some other
stuff, including this t-shirt
from P.S. Aeropostale.

And it's super comfy
and super light

and airy for all
the warm weather
we've been having recently.
-Mhm.

-And we were so
glad and so lucky we
got to meet all of you guys.
It was so fun.

And for those of you guys
we didn't get to meet,

there is a coupon code
down below that 20 percent

off everything, so
you guys can still

shop even though
you weren't there.

-Don't forget to give this
video a thumbs up, and comment

below where you guys want
us to do our next meetup.
It can be anywhere.
It would be fun.
We want to know.
And I think that's all we have--
-Mhm.

-So we'll see you
guys next week.
-Bye!
[MUSIC PLAYING]

-So yeah, I want the
ability to refill anything.
-What?

-If your bank account
is empty, you refill it.
If your glass is empty--
-Wha--
